        "subject": "LU-3319 lproc: seq file client side patch (fortestonly)",
        "message": "LU-3319 lproc: seq file client side patch (fortestonly)\n\nThis client side patch is to get rid of read/write_proc_t and only\nuse seq_file to adapt to 3.10 upstream kernel proc_dir_entry change.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly serverarch=x86_64 serverdistro=el6 serverbuildno=1601 clientarch=x86_64 clientdistro=el6\nSigned-off-by: Liu Ying <emoly.liu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ife8d37c80bd22dca2bc7c4d1f7b6cb5b86be36ed\n"
